Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大地上所有生命消失的審判之畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOST CANVAS 在天空展開的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哈迪斯城內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著聖鬥士天馬的冥王的兩位親信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙子神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬 為了你能夠將你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給正在繪製這幅恐怖的畫的亞倫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也將和你一起戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的不安感究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著天馬而去的這股邪惡而巨大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖戰 現在正向新的局面發展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(910,580}{\fad(500,0}第14話       死之森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那兩個傢伙跑得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼腳步都搖搖晃晃了？天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了的話 我就為了你休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 累的人是你吧 耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說夢話 我可沒事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉上不是寫著"讓我休息一會"嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 居然敢騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在打打鬧鬧了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要把你們兩個都丟下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 讓葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打鬧？誰會和這種傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 薩莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會潛入哈迪斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底地結束這場聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉大人 哈迪斯大人到底在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近完全看不到他的身影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪斯大人現在正在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心繪製LOST CANVAS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管太多了 切希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將哈迪斯大人軟禁在畫室裡 是為了他好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓他盡快丟棄骯髒的人類之心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為完全的冥王覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪斯大人的那個微笑到底有什麼含義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位大人正在那裡等候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普諾斯大人 達拿都斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召見我潘朵拉 不知有何要事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該記得 我們說過 會親手抹殺天馬座這事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到冥界三巨頭之一 拉達曼迪斯的小宇宙正在行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下達了什麼命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有讓拉達曼迪斯行動的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事我潘朵拉並不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是一種不值得傾注全部信賴的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們明明愚蠢 卻有狡猾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對人類時 應當過份謹慎些才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉也是很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些惹神明不悅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是沒什麼好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在天馬座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到我部分力量的冥鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會熱情地去迎接天馬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在200多年前的上一次聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜的聖鬥士們在我們面前就像嬰兒一樣無力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次聖戰一定要讓我們盡興才行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次像這樣面會教皇是多少年前了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諷刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我見面之時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是將有災難降於聖域之時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 本以為你坐上教皇之位後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就完全變遲鈍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來拳法還沒有衰退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那 不曾衰老的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再次覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的實力並不僅僅是白銀聖鬥士級別的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然老了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭壇星座白禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兄弟並肩戰鬥的那場聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿就像昨天一般歷歷在目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把黃金聖鬥士的資格讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為巨蟹座聖鬥士和你一同突入冥王軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們失去了許多的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最終保護了這大地上的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但本該成為教皇的你卻在兩百多年間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在背後默默支持著聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不喜歡上檯面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把一切都推給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對此深表歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本 祭壇座的使命便是輔助教皇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每當聖域有不穩的徵兆 你就會像這樣來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通過人馬座的希緒弗斯感受到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被某個巨大的小宇宙封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡神 修普諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 死神 達拿都斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為哈迪斯親信的他們有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道冥王軍發生了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他們是非常謹慎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次聖戰為了抓住他們的尾巴都費盡了力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希緒弗斯為了調查他們跑遍了各地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕雙子神是因此而記恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將被冥王所傷的希緒弗斯的靈魂封印到了某個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然雙子神已經開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬他們就令人擔心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次雖然被他們占了先機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次我們早有對策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不能預料到更先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗那雙子神也就是天方夜譚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就祈禱他們武運長遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子 難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家小弟真會給人添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬尼戈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道天馬的行蹤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來正要被派去大老遠的義大利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責看孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬他果然！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你小弟真讓我覺得心煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管故鄉被毀啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老頭又會煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇知道這事了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬前往哈迪斯城的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管這些雞零狗碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那小弟是哈迪斯的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用價值很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 別衝動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為小弟著想的心情 我也不是不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是接近哈迪斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空就越是被LOST CANVAS所覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慘不忍睹的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣和平的城鎮被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過這個鎮子馬上就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的故鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有這麼片森林嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好陰森恐怖的森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們必須前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣突破它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成森林的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起是不是就有股奇怪的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是什麼腐爛的氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骨頭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 花環被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 別跑那麼遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們都消失了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連讓葉都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你站住呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然耶人要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊跑一邊留在樹上的記號…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明記得這棵樹上也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮突然起火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸也變得很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來遲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為亞倫他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王軍真的把大家都殺害了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果我們還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬的血 好溫暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著呢 天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬你還活著 我們很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們嫉妒啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然跑進那麻煩的森林裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍臭漫天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那森林可不是人類的產物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也許比較適合我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會說抓天馬座 一會又說保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太會差遣人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚美詩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管風琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個白癡能在這種異常情況下若無其事地彈管風琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知您是否中意呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對您與摯愛親友們的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管風琴可不能停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點解放他們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是特地從冥界把他們帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得讓他們好好派上用場才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就算解放他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也只會腐爛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣豈不是更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要轟飛你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個傻孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他的血肉全部吸乾！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把那個管風琴想辦法毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是衝著這管風琴來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀了這管風琴會有什麼後果？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奉達拿都斯大人之命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護死亡森林的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.62,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納蘇（NASU）是拜火教（祆教）的女惡魔，以蒼蠅的形態出現。 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天究星的納蘇（NASU）維羅妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥鬥士嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來告訴聖鬥士先生您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那種程度的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是管風琴還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不能傷到分毫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這管風琴被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些和你一起長大情同兄弟的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變回普通的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也沒關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們不是很痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是在哭嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙竟然為所欲為利用他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他們被控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的靈魂並沒有墮落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們再咬狠一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬彗星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的小宇宙是傷不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒能保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能保護大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到天馬說過的宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的成為聖鬥士了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞倫他肯定也在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服都被血染髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有膽說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放過的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們闖入死之森林 迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄散著各種死之符號的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能聽見死者的聲音 從某個地方傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這個聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起令人懷念的我的故鄉嘉米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢 The lost canvas  冥王神話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能回到那天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:15.17,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘自 讚美詩的第23首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:15.17,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶和華是我的牧者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:21.52,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必不至缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:32.26,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他使我躺臥在青草地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:43.84,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領我在可安歇的水邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:54.46,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他使我的靈魂蘇醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:17:10.18,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為自己的名引導我走義路
